## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available data and projections, which are subject to change as new research emerges. The complexity of climate systems and the variability in regional impacts mean that predictions may not fully capture future realities. Additionally, the focus on developed countries may overlook the interconnectedness of global climate impacts, where changes in one region can have cascading effects on others.